OL,4,COfsted to visit English schools where
OL,5,Csexual abuse was reported
OL,6, Schools and colleges in England where
OL,7, students have reported incidences of
OL,8, sexual violence could be visited by
OL,9, inspectors from the regulator, Ofsted.
OL,11,FThe watchdog has announced it will
OL,12,Fvisit "a sample of schools and colleges
OL,13,Fwhere cases have been highlighted".
OL,15,FInspectors will assess how well schools
OL,16,Frespond, and support their pupils.
OL,18,FIt comes after more than 11,000 reports
OL,19,Fwere posted on the Everyone's Invited
OL,20,Fwebsite, where students can anonymously
OL,21,Fshare their experiences of abuse.
